snippet.title: The Last Plague: Blight - Official Trailer
snippet.description:
The official trailer for Original Studio's upcoming brutally challenging and realistic survival game The Last Plague: Blight.

Wishlist on Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1564600/

The game was renamed from "Blight" to "The Last Plague: Blight"
